# =============================================================================
# SETUP
# =============================================================================
#
# File Identity:
#   - Key: CODE-GIT-001
#   - Consumer: Git version control system
#   - Loader: Automatic - git reads .gitignore in each directory
#
# Related Files:
#   - Global: ~/.gitignore_global (user-wide ignores)
#   - Local: .git/info/exclude (repo-specific, not shared)
#   - Docs: https://git-scm.com/docs/gitignore
#
# Pattern Syntax:
#   - Blank lines are ignored
#   - Lines starting with # are comments
#   - ! negates a pattern (includes previously excluded)
#   - / at end means directory only
#   - * matches anything except /
#   - ** matches across directories
#   - ? matches single character
#
# =============================================================================
# END SETUP
